US Release Date: October 2025
Starring: Gabriela Andrada, Nicole Wallace, Gabriel Guevara
Synopsis: Jenna and Lion’s wedding leads to the long-awaited reunion between Noah and Nick years after their breakup. Nick’s inability to forgive Noah’s betrayal creates an insurmountable barrier between them. He, heir to his grandfather’s business empire, and she, just starting her career, resist rekindling the flame that still smolders within them. But after their paths have crossed again, will love prove stronger than resentment?
